messages.message: Hi team, not sure who the Jira admin is, but could we consider enabling the "Story Points" field on Jira tickets? It makes it easier to estimate time needed to complete a bunch of tickets over the course of several months :slightly_smiling_face:
we can do it potentially on a project by project basis. It's kind of noisy for the teams that don't use it which is why I took it out. Which project would you like to use it on?
